review.reviewBody: Great sandwiches as usual. The #11 and 27 are our go to and they never disappoint. The oatmeal raisin cookies are great too.

The number 18 and number 08 are good turkey sandwiches and some of our favourites to order. Their turkey is fresh tasting and is superior to deli turkey any day. Add hickory chips for some extra crunch. Portions are good and filling.
Number 22 is my go to and my husband loves the 07.
Best Vegetarian and Vegan sandwich options I've ever had.
Best sandwich in Vancouver! The Goofs leaving bad reviews don't know what they are talking about. The #4 is a vibe.
